727411f-c.title: Queens: Metropolitan Avenue - Himrod Street
727411f-c.text:
Metropolitan Avenue (tracks thereon) at the S.E. corner of
Himrod Street, showing two homes in this set of three views be-
longing to one Hetling. The smaller house perched on the hill
was demolished prior to 1934. H.C. Herring was the probable owner
from 1860 to 1873.
1922
Views 1,2 and 3
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
